# Cline Project Rules

## Memory Bank
This project uses a Cline Memory Bank in /memory-bank/.
At the start of every new session, read ALL files in memory-bank/ before doing anything.
Update activeContext.md and progress.md after completing any significant work.

## Code Style
- Flask app using factory pattern
- Follow existing blueprint structure for new routes
- Always parameterize SQL; never concatenate user input into queries
- Sanitize all user input before writing to Excel cells (use sanitize_cell())
- SECRET_KEY must always come from environment — never hardcode

## Security Rules (from Snyk/Bandit audit — 2026-06-23)
- seed_database() must only run in FLASK_ENV=development
- No bare except: pass — always log exceptions
- No hardcoded credentials anywhere in the codebase